The author conclude there story with those passage of show is importance of a inspiration Saeng gets under the hibiscus plant. Saeng, for the story am comforted by the hibiscus plant because it reminded her of home. The plant off the winter metaphorically explained: @CAPS1 attitude toward his new country and his driving test; the hibiscus plant on the winter is not as beautiful in the bitter cold, but it adapted and surviving, and returns to its beautiful state in the spring. Saeng is bitter about her new country and driving test, but is adapts, and will in inspired by the beautiful state of the hibiscus on the spring the try her test again. In conclusion, the author ended the story in that way to stress importance over the relationship between Saeng but the hibiscus plant.

